<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Online Championship</strong> - Up for the ultimate online championship? Challenge players from all over the world! Play Ranked Online matches to increase your Color-Qi level and become one of the Ultra Color Ranger grade players.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Story Mode</strong> - An action-packed adventure awaits! Defeat Greyus and his lieutenants, who threaten the chromatic balance on Earth. Enjoy it solo or with a friend in local co-operative play for the entire story.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sentai School</strong> - Learn the ropes of color rangers through a series of short challenges. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581440/extras/99f35a96422727ea5e714c15bfb2682d.poster.avif?t=1767080357\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581440/extras/99f35a96422727ea5e714c15bfb2682d.webm?t=1767080357\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581440/extras/99f35a96422727ea5e714c15bfb2682d.mp4?t=1767080357\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
